Bersa made both their Thunder & Firestorm models chambered in .380 & .22 long rifle. They are basically the same guns- but the FS has the very comfortable finger finger groove grips & the classic rounded trigger guard (that fits most holsters better) & they both have highly visible steel adjustable sights.

To me; the 2-Tone Bersa Firestorm (Black Frame with Silver Slide/Finger Groove Grips/Round Trigger Gd.) is their best looking .22.
 This pistol currently has it's mag safety residing in a plastic bag- & it only takes a few minutes to re-install if you so desire.
